# Testing Instructions

## Testing goals
- assert behavior, not implementation trivia
- cover edge cases and failure paths when behavior changes
- keep setup and assertions readable
- prefer local, stable tests over brittle global fixtures
- make omissions explicit when full coverage is not practical

## Coordination
- align new tests to `docs/agentic-workflow/06_test_spec.md` when that file exists
- preserve the writer-surface rule: this area is owned by `test-engineer`
